INSERT INTO ai_recommendations (artistProfileId, type, title, description, reasoning, confidenceScore, dataSources, status, priority, expiresAt, createdAt, updatedAt)
VALUES 
  (1, 'career_move', 'Automate Stream Milestone Celebrations', 'Set up a workflow to automatically thank fans when you hit streaming milestones. This increases engagement and builds stronger fan relationships.', 'Based on your growing fanbase and engagement patterns, automated milestone celebrations can increase fan retention by 23% according to platform data.', 85, '["Your streaming analytics", "Platform engagement data", "Industry best practices"]', 'pending', 8, DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL 7 DAY), NOW(), NOW()),
  (1, 'other', 'Enable Instant Payouts', 'You have earnings available. Enable instant payouts to access your funds in 1 hour for just a 1% fee.', 'Your earnings balance shows available funds. Instant payouts provide quick access to your money when you need it.', 90, '["Your earnings balance", "Payout settings"]', 'pending', 9, DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL 3 DAY), NOW(), NOW()),
  (1, 'marketing_strategy', 'Upload to Third-Party Platforms', 'Your recent tracks are performing well on BAP. Consider distributing to Spotify and Apple Music to maximize reach and revenue.', 'Your BAP streaming data shows strong performance. Expanding to additional platforms could increase your total streams by 40-60% based on similar artists.', 78, '["Your BAP analytics", "Cross-platform performance data", "Similar artist benchmarks"]', 'pending', 7, DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL 14 DAY), NOW(), NOW());
